## 7. Employee Communication

### 7.1 How to Request a New AI Tool

Employees who wish to use an AI tool not currently in {{ business_name }}'s Sanctioned AI register must:

1. **Check the Sanctioned AI Register** to confirm the tool is not already approved
2. **Submit an AI Procurement Request** to {{ ai_governance_contact if ai_governance_contact else "the AI governance contact" }}
3. **Do not process** any {{ business_name }} data through the tool until approval is granted
4. **Await confirmation** — standard evaluations are completed within 15 business days

