## 8. Metrics and KPIs

{{ business_name }} will track the following metrics to measure Shadow AI program effectiveness:

| Metric | Target | Measurement Frequency |
|--------|--------|-----------------------|
| Shadow AI discovery rate | Decreasing quarter-over-quarter | Quarterly |
| Time-to-detection | < 14 days from first use to discovery | Quarterly |
| Time-to-remediate (Critical/High) | < 48 hours from discovery to block | Per incident |
| Time-to-remediate (Medium/Low) | < 30 days from discovery to resolution | Per incident |
| Employee AI request rate | Increasing (indicates culture of compliance) | Quarterly |
| Tolerated-to-sanctioned conversion rate | > 50% of tolerated tools proceed to approval | Quarterly |
| Repeat offender rate | < 5% of employees discovered more than once | Annually |
| Sanctioned AI register completeness | 100% of known AI tools catalogued | Quarterly |

